] them through <model operations>?

  <core_thesis> :=
    <multimodal AI> [does not simply translate
] <text> into <image>;
    it [routes
] both through <shared artificial semantics>,
    thereby [weakening
] the inherited <text/image distinction> at the level of <technical substrate>.
</Initial_Interpretation>


